item.title: Merry Christmas
item.description: MERRY CHRISTMAS AND A HAPPY NEW YEAR! FELIZ NATAL E PROSPERO ANO NOVA! Merry Christmas In 2023, our teams finished over 38000 user stories in more than 10 large-scale software projects of the highest strategic importance for our worldwide clients. Both our engineering hubs in Hamburg and Lisbon are thriving. Our Portuguese team has moved into a new office in the heart of Lisbon, and now at the end of the year, we are already looking for new spaces.

item.title: Merry Christmas
item.description: This year, we’ve chosen to support our neighbors: Kiezhelden represents the social commitment of FC St. Pauli. Many individuals and groups from the fan scene and club departments are deeply involved in social areas, shaping the club’s image. FC St. Pauli itself takes responsibility for society, undertaking social and sociopolitical projects and events or providing support for them.
